      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 20:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>爱德华·琼斯 (Edward Jones) 首席执行官：尽管通货膨胀，客户仍支出</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-10/edward-jones-ceo-on-asset-allocation-strategy-crypto-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[爱德华·琼斯首席执行官彭妮·彭宁顿表示，尽管通胀上升，公司的客户仍在消费。彭宁顿在彭博电视上发表讲话时还讨论了她在当前经济环境下的资产配置策略，并补充说爱德华·琼斯正在对加密货币采取观望态度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-10/edward-jones-ceo-on-asset-allocation-strategy-crypto-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 19:49:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Blue Owl 以 3.35 亿美元的价格击败其他贷款人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/blue-owl-beat-other-lenders-on-price-for-335-million-facility</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，Blue Owl Capital Inc. 击败了所有其他贷款机构，向天然气服务商 Dresser Utility Solutions 提供了 3.35 亿美元的信贷额度，因为该公司能够提供较低的定价。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-10/blue-owl-beat-other-lenders-on-price-for-335-million-facility</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Apr 2024 19:41:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
